Use Ublock to hide elements from Encounter Types. These items are hidden based on their position in the list - if the list gets updated, you'll need to update the filter

Use browser's devtools to locate the item to hide. It should look similar to this:

##select#visitTypeDD > option:nth-of-type(5)

Use ublock to create a filter for each item to hide:

<yoursubdomain>.patagoniaemr.com##select#visitTypeDD > option:nth-of-type(5)
<yoursubdomain>.patagoniaemr.com##select#visitTypeDD > option:nth-of-type(14)
